{"tid":1932882,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"兩人確診武漢肺炎　紐約證交所下周一關閉交易大廳","createTime":"2020-03-19T03:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T09:25:05.000Z","uid":20272,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c23d7a92be6a620f2ef9b0e9bf5e34bde8e96e46","tid":1932882,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/202003/72223431_521698065061451_5069956095447924736_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F202003%2F72223431_521698065061451_5069956095447924736_n.jpg&h=640cf4fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受疫情影響，紐約證券交易所將於下周一（3月23日）開始，暫時關閉交易大廳並轉為全電子交易。  公告指，紐交所在紐約的股票和期權交易大廳，以及在三藩市的期權交易場所都將關閉。  公司向交易員的通知中提到，有兩人在周一檢測時對武漢肺炎病毒呈陽性，分別為一名紐約證交所的僱員和一名交易員，兩人本周被禁止進入該建築物，他們上次身處現場是在上周五。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-19-2020/61027?fbclid=IwAR1JChHsdCEB5h4gVNFaCSDyWKpFaIgf87ehKoGVGDzB8ytCAh00r-zzz-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F03-19-2020%2F61027%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1JChHsdCEB5h4gVNFaCSDyWKpFaIgf87ehKoGVGDzB8ytCAh00r-zzz-I&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=23eb9621\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-19-2020/61027?fbclid=IwAR1JChHsdCEB5h4gVNFaCSDyWKpFaIgf87ehKoGVGDzB8ytCAh00r-zzz-I</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2020<br />\n<br />\n美股個市會唔會有影響？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60d44dc7044893ece54bdddadac4993ef2898a7","tid":1932882,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:38:26.000Z","msg":"道指又趺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672d9a45e72e7e6c75b86db6e1780131be94a443","tid":1932882,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:39:23.000Z","msg":"大檸樂"},{"pid":"0cfa97e9994149c3c6ae9250ad854d1d7d38ec29","tid":1932882,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"係咪玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9972d89c9ca0a138aa596e9390303fec8b16dab3","tid":1932882,"uid":106247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:46:47.000Z","msg":"用得全電子交易<br />\n之後係咪可以炒哂班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正無佢地都交易到"},{"pid":"823e63fde4bc2230f8311f54da580b1286c656d4","tid":1932882,"uid":177243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:46:53.000Z","msg":"另類救市方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2381583a77dad4e9f4abfeb642e7c772e6c324e4","tid":1932882,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"今晚又熔斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756ee51676882a6e3907a5c59b3023e798273330","tid":1932882,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"交滴現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18fc2b82be3bcb5c7b2c196afd7deaf5583d75f","tid":1932882,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:25:05.000Z","msg":"交疫現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}